helpdesk_ticket.subject: Reports delayed and uncertainty about the sample integrity
helpdesk_ticket.description_html:
Dear Pharmeasy customer care team,

My mothers sample was collected yesterday morning. It has been almost 40 hours now and I haven't received the full reports yet. Have ordered similar tests before and it has not taken more than 12-16 hours ever. This has also exceeded the usual claimed time of 30 hours. Given the scenario, I suspect the integrity of the sample or a possible mix-up. I ABSOLUTELY DO NOT trust the reports being generated and would like to request a sample re-collection as soon as possible.
I hope this is not repeated again.

Sincerely,
Digvijay 

--
Sincerely,
Digvijay L. Prakash
